OL,3,CArchitects and regulatory body under
OL,4,Cscrutiny for work on Grenfell
OL,6,FThe Architects Registration Board
OL,7,F(ARB) has received a formal complaint
OL,8,Ffrom the Good Law Project over its
OL,9,Ffailure to investigate architects who
OL,10,Fworked at Studio E, the architecture
OL,11,Ffirm at the centre of the Grenfell
OL,12,FTragedy.
OL,14,FARB is a public corporation of the
OL,15,FMinistry of Housing, Communities, and
OL,16,FLocal Government. It regulates the
OL,17,Farchitects' profession in the UK to
OL,18,Fensure consistent standards of conduct
OL,19,Fand practice.
