OL,4,Cscrutiny for work on Grenfell
OL,6,FThe Good Law Project has been pushing
OL,7,Ffor the ARB to take enforcement action
OL,8,Ffollowing the Grenfell fire in 2017
OL,9,Fthat killed 72 people.
OL,11,FThe campaign group hopes that this
OL,12,Fcomplaint will not only be upheld, but
OL,13,Falso set a precedent so that other
OL,14,Fpeople in cladded buildings can file a
OL,15,Fcomplaint against their architects.
OL,17,FThe Good Law Project's campaign is
OL,18,Fbeing supported by some of the
OL,19,Ffamilies impacted by the fire and
OL,20,Fcomes following the publication of the
OL,21,Fsecond part of the inquiry.
