OL,6,FThe families of Amna Mahmoud Idris,
OL,7,FAmal Ahmedin, and three-year-old Amaya
OL,8,FAhmedin, all of whom died on the 19th
OL,9,FFloor of Grenfell Tower, said: "These
OL,10,Farchitects were responsible for the
OL,11,Farchitectural safety of our and our
OL,12,Ffamilies' homes.
OL,14,F"Yet none of their partners or
OL,15,Femployees had the relevant knowledge,
OL,16,Fexperience or skills needed to work on
OL,17,Fa high-rise cladding project.
OL,26,@qD@`OU
