OL,3,CArchitects and regulatory body under
OL,4,Cscrutiny for work on Grenfell
OL,6,F"They let us and our loved ones down.
OL,7,FEven more sickeningly, they complained
OL,8,Fthat they weren't being paid enough.
OL,9,FThose who profited from their own
OL,10,Fincompetence and negligence at the
OL,11,FGrenfell fire may be held to account
OL,12,Ftoday.
OL,14,F"But we, the bereaved families, will
OL,15,Fhave to live with their mistakes for
OL,16,Fthe rest of our lives."
