OL,3,CArchitects and regulatory body under
OL,4,Cscrutiny for work on Grenfell
OL,6,FAn ARB spokesperson told ITV News, "We
OL,7,Fhave been monitoring the Grenfell
OL,8,FTower Inquiry closely since it was
OL,9,Festablished, but we were obliged to
OL,10,Fwait until the Grenfell Tower Inquiry
OL,11,FPhase Two Report was published before
OL,12,Fundertaking any formal investigative
OL,13,Factivities.
OL,15,F"Following the publication of that
OL,16,Freport, formal investigations have
OL,17,Fcommenced into whether any architects
OL,18,Finvolved in the refurbishment of the
OL,19,FTower might be guilty of a
OL,20,Fdisciplinary offence under the
OL,21,FArchitects Code.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
