OL,3,CArchitects and regulatory body under
OL,4,Cscrutiny for work on Grenfell
OL,6,F"The Grenfell Tower fire was a
OL,7,Fnational tragedy and is rightly
OL,8,Fconsidered one of the UK's worst
OL,9,Fmodern disasters, and we are sensitive
OL,10,Fto the strong public interest of
OL,11,Ftaking appropriate action without
OL,12,Fdelay."
OL,14,F"The investigations must be conducted
OL,15,Fproperly if they are to be effective,
OL,16,Fand can be complex, particularly when
OL,17,Fthey take place in the background of
OL,18,Fpotential criminal proceedings which
OL,19,Fmust not be prejudiced.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/7
