OL,3,CArchitects and regulatory body under
OL,4,Cscrutiny for work on Grenfell
OL,6,F"It is ARB's policy to not comment on
OL,7,Fthe detail of investigations until or
OL,8,Funless they reach a public hearing of
OL,9,Four Professional Conduct Committee, so
OL,10,Fthat the Committee can make an
OL,11,Findependent decision based on the
OL,12,Fevidence available. Information
OL,13,Fregarding forthcoming hearings is
OL,14,Fpublished to our website."
OL,16,FStudio E, who entered voluntary
OL,17,Fliquidation in 2020, are yet to
OL,18,Frespond to ITV News. The Grenfell
OL,19,Finquiry report found that Studio E
OL,20,Ffailed to meet the standards of a
OL,21,Freasonable competent architect.
